reviewText: Just plain good entertainment. Nevermind that the hunting is awesome and makes you crazy for the summer to be over!

He's my favorite hunting personality because he seems just a regular guy.  I've met him twice at various outdoor shows and he is very humble and enjoys talking to people.  I enjoy watching all of the extras with him and the other guys.  He lives the lifestyle I would love to live.  I'm a hunter.  A Bone Collector!
